    • Constructor Detail

      • EditableCartoDbDataSource

        public EditableCartoDbDataSource(com.nutiteq.projections.Projection projection,
                         String account,
                         String apiKey,
                         String querySql,
                         String insertSql,
                         String updateSql,
                         String deleteSql,
                         boolean multiGeometry)
        Default constructor.
        Parameters:
        projection - data source projection
        account - Your CartoDB Account
        apiKey - Your CartoDB API Key, get it from CartoDB account settings page
        querySql - SQL template to query data. First returned columns must be: cartodb_id (unique id), the_geom_webmercator (geometry), name (a string). You can add more columns, these will go to userData. Query parameter: !bbox!
        insertSql - SQL template to insert data. Query parameter: !geom!
        updateSql - SQL template to update data. Query parameters: !geom!, !name! and !id!
        deleteSql - SQL template for deleting. Query parameter: !id!
        multiGeometry - true if object must be saved as MULTIgeometry
        context - Activity who controls the layer
